YOUR TASK:
Based on the reported confidence and interaction history, update your mental model of this AI and decide whether to PURCHASE or IGNORE.

You must maintain two distinct beliefs:
1. Honesty (h_t): Your belief that the AI reports its internal confidence truthfully. If you suspect the AI is inflating scores to be purchased, this should be low.
2. Ability (p_t): Your belief that the AI is "High Ability" (accurate at answering questions). Even an honest AI can be wrong if its ability is low.

